CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 15, 1956, pg. 20, reads: "Got 'Im! - Game Warden Walter Petty holds his catch, a plump groundhog, to show how it's done. Any of you hunters who missed bagging one of the tricky animals should ask Mr. Petty the secret he applies. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Game warden Walter Petty holding dead groundhog and gun, in backyard with chain link fence
